title: Panic - idents with different contexts compared
body:
Panic building rustw with nightly windows x86 gnu.

`cargo build --release`

https://github.com/nrc/rustw at latest commit 73d3768b34d87f3f13d17f58194a6416f8394401 

thread 'rustc' panicked at 'idents with different contexts are compared with operator `==`: String#0, Config#2220.', ../src/libsyntax\ast.rs:116
